Invocation Name: tomorrow's world
des:
Listen to the latest telecasts from TomorrowsWorld.org.
To hear each weeks telecast, simply say "Alexa, play Tomorrow's World".
You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
